name: RIO_PEXPLE TXURISM 04
description:
We are observers, explosive, needy, aggressive, noisy, sticky, warm, gossipers, dancers, drunks, tightrope walkers, nomads.
It's never okay, but it's okay. 4 governors arrested? all right. Melicias growing without cold? We can handle it. Contaminated drinking water? relax, let's go to the beach.

We accept everything, we just don't accept that we are the same.
